ai-personal-assistant/
│
├── main.py                # Main script to run the assistant in terminal mode
├── app.py                 # Flask web interface for the assistant
├── voice_recognition.py   # Handles voice input
├── text_to_speech.py      # Handles text-to-speech output
├── command_handler.py     # Processes and executes commands
├── weather_api.py         # Fetches weather data
├── reminders.py           # Manages reminders
├── todo.py                # Manages to-do list (optional)
├── jokes.py               # Fetches and tells jokes (optional)
├── templates/             # Folder for Flask HTML templates
│   └── index.html         # HTML file for the web interface
└── requirements.txt       # List of dependencies
